comments: Anderson (MEM) jumps forward into Burks' (NYK) body and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) signals for a timeout as Barrett (NYK) and Gibson (NYK) trap Morant (MEM), but before any possible held ball.
Valanciunas (MEM) and Gibson (NYK) come together off ball and marginal contact occurs.
Anderson (MEM) loses control of the ball upon receiving the throw-in and any contact with Randle (NYK) is incidental.
Burks (NYK) is out of bounds when he receives the pass.
Anderson (MEM) moves alongside of Randle's (NYK) path to the basket and makes clean contact with the ball when he reaches in.  The contact to the body is marginal.
Barrett (NYK) moves alongside of Morant's (MEM) path to the basket and absorbs the contact as he makes the pass.
Gibson (NYK) engages with Valanciunas (MEM) during the rebound but does not affect his ability to get to the ball.
Brooks (MEM) jumps toward Barrett (NYK) and makes contact to his arm while he is in his jump shooting motion.
Gibson (NYK) makes contact to Morant's (MEM) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) maintains a legal guarding position during Randle's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Gibson (NYK) dislodges Valanciunas (MEM) from his position as he grabs the rebound.
Morant (MEM) moves toward Barrett (NYK) and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Morant (MEM) stops short and releases from the contact with Burks (NYK).
Burks (NYK) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball as he defends Morant (MEM).  Morant has an arm placed against Burks but he does not dislodge him from his position during the loose ball.
Randle (NYK) makes contact to Morant's (MEM) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
As Valanciunas (MEM) makes the pass, marginal contact occurs with Burks (NYK).
Anderson (MEM) has an arm in Randle's (NYK) path and the contact is marginal as the two players get their arms tangled briefly.
Quickley (NYK) is never in the lane for longer than three seconds before exiting.
Valanciunas (MEM) makes contact with the ball before incidental body contact occurs with Randle (NYK) during his driving shot attempt.
Anderson (MEM) grabs Randle's (NYK) arm and affects his ability to get to the loose ball.
Bullock (NYK) makes foot to foot contact with Allen (MEM) that affects his jump shot attempt.
Noel (NYK) jumps into Anderson (MEM) and makes contact to the body that affects his jump shot attempt.
Allen (MEM) commits a take foul on Randle (NYK).
Valanciunas (MEM) steps into the lane before the release of the free throw.
Anderson (MEM) commits a take foul on Burks (NYK).
Allen (MEM) commits a take foul on Quickley (NYK).
